resource/Juan_Bautista_Alvarado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The New Orleans Pelicans guard scored 10 points in a key stretch of the third quarter where Puerto Rico took control of the game.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.428815113376679e-32, \"text\": \"New Orleans Pelicans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Orleans_Pelicans\"}, {\"begin\": 1167, \"end\": 1178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9958001014098438, \"rank\": 0.004217487443969391, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished with 23 points, six rebounds, and two steals for a 23 efficiency while shooting 9-for-14 from the field and 4-for-6 from downtown.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the second-leading scorer in the San Juan Olympic Qualifying Tournament, averaging 16 points on the strength of his 29-point game against Italy in the group phase and his 23-point effort Sunday night.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9995146354942187, \"rank\": 0.00043451797667669486, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alvarado connected on 50 percent of his shots from the floor (22-for-44), 50 percent from thre